OL,3,CAngry locals vow to fight plans for
OL,4,C'disgraceful' giant Devon solar farm
OL,6,FITV News reporter Sam Blackledge looks
OL,7,Fat plans for a new solar farm in Devon
OL,9,FHundreds of people packed into a
OL,10,Fpublic meeting near Holsworthy in
OL,11,FDevon to voice their opposition to
OL,12,Fplans to build what would be one of
OL,13,Fthe biggest solar farms in Europe.
OL,15,FDevelopers say the Beacon Solar
OL,16,Fproject - which would cover around
OL,17,F2,700 acres of farmland - would reduce
OL,18,Freliance on fossil fuels.
