OL,3,CAngry locals vow to fight plans for
OL,4,C'disgraceful' giant Devon solar farm
OL,6,FBut campaigners have vowed to fight
OL,7,Fthe plans, insisting they are
OL,8,Funnecessary and unsustainable.
OL,10,FSir Geoffrey Cox, Conservative MP for
OL,11,FTorridge and Tavistock, told the
OL,12,Fmeeting the developer is threatening
OL,13,Fto "invade" the local community.
