OL,3,CAngry locals vow to fight plans for
OL,4,C'disgraceful' giant Devon solar farm
OL,6,FSir Geoffrey said: "We will devote
OL,7,Fevery ounce of energy to mount one
OL,8,Fhuge effort in combating this alien
OL,9,Fproposal that is to be imposed upon us
OL,10,F- not by the democratic consent of
OL,11,Fpeople here - but by the fiat of the
OL,12,FSecretary of State, who has decided on
OL,13,Fa policy that, in my view, makes no
OL,14,Fsense at all."
