OL,3,CAngry locals vow to fight plans for
OL,4,C'disgraceful' giant Devon solar farm
OL,6,FPenny Mills, chair of the Devon branch
OL,7,Fof the Campaign to Protect Rural
OL,8,FEngland, said: "It's the most
OL,9,Foutrageous, horrendous proposal. We
OL,10,Fare strongly opposed to any such
OL,11,Fscheme, and we will be spearheading
OL,12,Fthe campaign to try to put a stop to
OL,13,Fit."
OL,15,FGallileo Empower, the company behind
OL,16,FBeacon Solar, says it would generate
OL,17,Fmore than 100 megawatts of energy per
OL,18,Fyear.
