OL,3,CAngry locals vow to fight plans for
OL,4,C'disgraceful' giant Devon solar farm
OL,6,FIt would cover 2,700 acres, around
OL,7,Ffour square miles, making it one of
OL,8,Fthe largest solar farms in Europe.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Gallileo Empower said:
OL,11,F"Climate change is accepted as being
OL,12,Fone of the greatest threats to society
OL,13,Fin general. By combining renewable
OL,14,Fenergy generation with robust habitat
OL,15,Fmanagement and species protection,
OL,16,Fprojects like Beacon Solar are part of
OL,17,Fthe solution ` tackling climate change
OL,18,Fwhile protecting and enhancing local
OL,19,Fecosystems."
