OL,7,FEnergy Security and Net Zero said:
OL,8,F"The biggest threat to agriculture and
OL,9,Fnature is the climate crisis.
OL,11,F"Solar is the cheapest power ` getting
OL,12,Fus off fossil fuels and delivering
OL,13,Fenergy security so we can get bills
OL,14,Fdown for good.
OL,16,F"All projects are subject to rigorous
OL,17,Fplanning processes, and the views of
OL,18,Fthe local community must be taken into
OL,19,Faccount."
